title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Get Double Rewards and More from Gerald
content:
Gerald doesn’t talk much because he prefers to let his reputation speak for him. Solidify his legacy by assisting him in Gerald Contact Missions (including his exit strategy in Gerald’s Last Play) for 2X GTA$ and RP.

Completing three Gerald’s Last Play missions will satisfy the Weekly Challenge and result in an extra GTA$100,000.
